## Package Overview

`SundusGenome1` is an R package that demonstrates:

- S4 object-oriented programming in R  
- Integration of C++ using Rcpp  
- Basic genome data modeling and computation  

The package provides:

| Component | Description |
|---|---|
| **`Genome` (S4 class)** | Stores genome name, number of chromosomes, and number of proteins |
| **`avgProteinPerCh()`** | Computes average proteins per chromosome (rounded) |
| **Rcpp functions** | High-performance C++ functions (`sumCpp`, `add_vecs`, `subset_vec`) |

